caption:
Carbides bits only file ONE direction (typically)

The special blades/flutes are cut in 1 direction that's specific for right or left hand use

RIGHT HAND: run the efile in FORWARD towards the left

LEFT HAND: run the efile in REVERSE towards the right

Watch our full carbide barrel tutorial on YouTube for more pro efiling tips - link in bio! 💋
